{"tid":1999954,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[長文] 點解媽咪麵係財經台第一股神KOL？","createTime":"2020-05-03T13:50:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-05T12:36:02.000Z","uid":70194,"like":178,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":65,"replies":[{"pid":"294b836a00356ea54861b85c05f47d8b9494ded8","tid":1999954,"uid":70194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T13:50:15.000Z","msg":"依幾日見到有唔同既人出左POST分析媽咪麵係咪燈，但其實部份就過份片面，有部份就純粹針對個股. 財經台巴打其實最關心既係大DODO佢點睇恆指，<strong>因為大部份人都係玩恆指既牛熊輪</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n我嘗試搵返大DODO過去兩年幾開POST，當中特別挑選果期比較有意義既POST，對應返恆指一D明顯既轉勢位. 睇下大DODO分析有幾準.<br />\n<br />\n廢話少講，睇下圖&mdash;<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uVbqS55.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuVbqS55.jpg&h=92701b37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n圖中既數目字標記係相對應以下由大DODO開既POST&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n1. 大家扣好安全帶未?????????????   [2018年2月13日]<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/559278/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/559278/page/1</a><br />\n按: 大DODO當日出POST話準備沖落谷底，跟住恆指暴力夾升左半個月. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"color: gold;\">[中]</span><br />\n<br />\n2. 媽咪麵轉身變  已變牛戰士  以CALL凝聚力量救世人跳出生天!!!!!!!!!!!! [2018年6月7日]<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/692719/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/692719/page/1</a><br />\n按: 大DODO當日唱出經典美少女戰士既歌詞，表示自己由熊轉牛，睇大牛市. 跟住恆指發生咩事大家好清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"color: gold;\">[中]</span><br />\n<br />\n3. 我都決定走了！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/887029/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/887029/page/1</a> [2018年11月2日]<br />\n按: 大DODO果期一路扮自己係熊軍, 但其實係睇恆指升，結果輸到趴街 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"color: gold;\">[中]</span><br />\n<br />\n4. 想問今朝笑尻我班友去哂邊？？！  [2018年12月27日]<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/957705/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/957705/page/1</a><br />\n按: 大DODO搵人學牛叫. 姐係表示熊軍黎緊會威威. 結果恆指2019年開始暴力夾升 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"color: gold;\">[中]</span><br />\n<br />\n5. 一路食牛仔安格斯   一路嘰嘰聲咁對住m記仔笑   真係享受～～～～<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1107504/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1107504/page/1</a>  [2019年4月15日]<br />\n按: 大DODO 食M記. 俾利害既網友發現佢買左牛 (睇返top comment). 跟住恆指又展開新一輪跌市<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"color: gold;\">[中]</span><br />\n<br />\n6. 黎啦黎啦黎啦黎啦鼓啦黎啦！！！！！千跌終於黎啦！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1506574/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1506574/page/1</a>  [2019年8月26日]<br />\n按: 大DODO話有熊市就有我. 跟住恆指慢慢chok住上. <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"color: gold;\">[中]</span><br />\n<br />\n7. 考考大家   淨係香港沙士就萬八點   咁全中國沙士會幾多點呢!!!!!?   [2020年1月20日]<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1830753/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1830753/page/1</a><br />\n按: 大DODO 係暫時罕有地見到佢開POST睇跌. 而個市又真係進入熊市. 今次大DODO睇唔中！！令到一眾財經台巴打以為大DODO破燈.  [<span style=\"color: red;\">唔中</span>]"},{"pid":"0bf60704421f2a99b3d89dd8cbfea63e91253810","tid":1999954,"uid":81150,"like":257,"dislike":8,"score":249,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T13:52:54.000Z","msg":"咪咁啦你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br /