gmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"color: gold;\">[中]</span><br />\n<br />\n5. 一路食牛仔安格斯   一路嘰嘰聲咁對住m記仔笑   真係享受～～～～<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1107504/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1107504/page/1</a>  [2019年4月15日]<br />\n按: 大DODO 食M記. 俾利害既網友發現佢買左牛 (睇返top comment). 跟住恆指又展開新一輪跌市<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"color: gold;\">[中]</span><br />\n<br />\n6. 黎啦黎啦黎啦黎啦鼓啦黎啦！！！！！千跌終於黎啦！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1506574/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1506574/page/1</a>  [2019年8月26日]<br />\n按: 大DODO話有熊市就有我. 跟住恆指慢慢chok住上. <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"color: gold;\">[中]</span><br />\n<br />\n7. 考考大家   淨係香港沙士就萬八點   咁全中國沙士會幾多點呢!!!!!?   [2020年1月20日]<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1830753/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1830753/page/1</a><br />\n按: 大DODO 係暫時罕有地見到佢開POST睇跌. 而個市又真係進入熊市. 今次大DODO睇唔中！！令到一眾財經台巴打以為大DODO破燈.  [<span style=\"color: red;\">唔中</span>]"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T15:09:00.000Z","msg":"應該要計埋今日，燈到跌1000點 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44ad419ec5d1a487b18dc5b8495ce350ab4fdd6a","tid":1999954,"uid":70194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T07:20:42.000Z","msg":"麵神 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83431bc7973ce8766bc879ae4094abdaa979275e","tid":1999954,"uid":251458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e7ab703317d39ac6ed9b0e26c54f377f59